	<h4>Meetings minutes</h4>
	<p>
		You can find here <a href= "/kleine_seminar/notes/">the note of the meeting</a>. The material has probably a high chance of being error-filled here,
		but the margins content some hastily scribbled snippets of the discussion we had in the seminar and might prove interesting!
	</p>
	
	
	<h2> Contact </h2>
	
	<p>If you have inquiries about the Kleine seminar, the easiest would be to contact me with the information below, but contacting 
	any other member is a valid strategy!</p>
